<h2>Setup</h2>

<p class="medium-7 large-5">
  Repurposed from the <a href="https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/drawinglayer" target="_blank">Google Maps Drawing Manager</a>, Selections allow you to draw shapes on your map instance and send that selection data to your parent scopes. This allows users to select areas on the map to interact with.  To use the selections API you must add the "drawing" library to your app like so:
</p>

